    dc:description "FIGURES 283–285. Phaeoxantha (Euphaeoxantha) lindemannae (Mandl), HT and AT, from Rio Negro, Amazonas, Brazil (ZSM). 283–284—habitus: 283—♂, 24 mm, HT; 284—♀, 26 mm, AT; 285—labels of the HT. Bars = 1 mm. Image credit Michael Balke." ;
