    dc:description "FIGURES 286–291. Phaeoxantha (Euphaeoxantha) lindemannae (Mandl), all from Rio Negro, Manaus, Brazil (CCJM). 286—head, ♂; 287–288—labrum: 287—♂; 288—♀; 289–290—mandibles: 289—♂; 290—♀; 291—aedeagus. Bars = 1 mm." ;
