    dc:description "FIGURES 292–295. Phaeoxantha (Euphaeoxantha) lindemannae (Mandl), all from Rio Negro, Manaus, Brazil (CCJM). 292—pronotum, ♂; 293–295—elytra: 293—♂; 294—♂; 295—♀. Bars = 1 mm." ;
